participant.subtitle: Mwafika pa tsamba loyamba la Intake24.

participant.info:
Ngati mwayitanidwa kuti mutenge nawo gawo mukafukufuku wa Intake24 mumayenera kupatsidwa link.

Chonde onani ngati mwayitanidwa kuti mutenge nawo gawo. Ngati simukudziwa bwino, chonde funsani gulu loyang'anira kafukufuku uyu.

generateUser.400: Zomwe mwapereka zotsimikiza kuti ndinu munthu ndi zolakwika.
generateUser.403: Kafukufuku {surveyId} salola kuti ogwiritsa ntchito azipangire okha nambala zolowera.
generateUser.429: Ogwritsa ntchito watsopano wapangidwa kumene, yesani nthawi yina.
generateUser.subtitle: Uyu ndi kafukufuku opezaka kwa wina aliyense,mutha kupanga nawo mwaulere.
generateUser.info1: Sankhani 'njira yolowera' kuti mupange njira mawu olowera. Lembani mawuwa ngati mukufuna kupitiliza kafukufuku nthawi yina.
generateUser.info2: Kafukufuku uyu atenga pafupi fupi mphindi 15.
generateUser.info3: Ngati mwaseka tsamba la makina lolowera ku kafukufukuyu, muthakubwelerako kugwiritsira ntchito ichi {action}.
